wikipedia_page.main: Miranda Elizabeth Louise Macmillan, Countess of Stockton (née Quarry; 27 May 1947 – 18 March 2020) was a British socialite and fashion model.

response: Diana Lloyd was married before to Richard Bridges St. John Quarry. They have a daughter Miranda, Countess of Stockton (1947–2020).
